{"tid":943320,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"深水埗派錢係行為不檢 咁佐敦派錢呢？","createTime":"2018-12-16T12:44:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T03:03:13.000Z","uid":218914,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c9c34e199c602386e2dcb7be98e490b7379ea823","tid":943320,"uid":218914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T12:44:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ovULkKu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FovULkKu.jpg&h=7c1c77c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4345fa9e49704e34889630f58d16cb1cfa6eeea2","tid":943320,"uid":71433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T12:46:35.000Z","msg":"我鍾意啊 吹咩"},{"pid":"61fe6a9956713aad8333e7a92e92bbb80508c6ae","tid":943320,"uid":182930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T12:46:57.000Z","msg":"頭100名市民"},{"pid":"b3858b9455aacee7eb21be8e62413df485d97ce6","tid":943320,"uid":88022,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T12:55:38.000Z","msg":"我個仔答特首係周星馳都做到警察<br />\n我派錢會唔得?!<br />\n成堆律師企起度 stand by 住派<br />\n你咬我食呀?!"},{"pid":"2693717b0e9a72b01f08887895168c8791dd83ca","tid":943320,"uid":218914,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T13:28:07.000Z","msg":"call埋我皮膚科醫生洗介賴<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Go5bgxj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGo5bgxj.jpg&h=e5104ad8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba088fffa454b95109856bd2881bee304eb63bb5","tid":943320,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T01:10:24.000Z","msg":"仲重要係會唔會引起混亂<br />\n警察要防止人踩人<br />\n唔好好似1993年蘭桂坊 celebrate 新年咁"},{"pid":"02d640993368c7ff4f33ee50b95583a47facc4e4","tid":943320,"uid":10833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61fe6a9956713aad8333e7a92e92bbb80508c6ae","tid":943320,"uid":182930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T12:46:57.000Z","msg":"頭100名市民"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T01:36:42.000Z","msg":"可以平均"},{"pid":"1889e6bb86202816570156b62baf11d9117ac2bb","tid":943320,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T02:27:04.000Z","msg":"除左今次幣少實地派真錢外，<br />\n社會上都發展左好多文明方式的派錢方法。<br />\n<br />\n但看歷史，<br />\n只要係為宣傳而派錢的方式，<br />\n最終都會令社會大部分人受損，<br />\n少數人受惠，<br />\n多數窮人更慘。<br />\n<br />\n文明派錢例子<br />\n<br />\n<strong>地產商派錢：樓市升值</strong>，業主賺到笑。大家都知禍害深遠。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>金融機構派錢：股票股市又升值</strong>，股民發發。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>IT界派錢：炒iphone，比特幣暴升</strong>（比特幣的匿名特性，吸引好多黑客做電腦加密勒索，如 wannacry，同毒販做毒品交易，避開警方拘捕）<br />\n各項抽獎活動<br />\n<br />\n理由<br />\n<strong>羊毛出自羊身上，派錢受惠通常係少數。</strong>但<strong>背後就係想宣傳，希望氹大量水魚傻仔，用貴價買佢產品</strong>。呢類派錢活動，只係<strong>化左妝的澳門賭場。</strong> 所以最終<strong>社會整體一定係蝕多賺少。</strong><br />\n<br />\n所以實際係，<strong>社會越多派錢活動，窮人會更多</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n最後想講澳門政府派錢<br />\n<br />\n澳門派錢：表面人人受惠，實際只有澳門人受惠。班澳門吸引大量的香港人和大陸人傻仔去賭，不少賭到傾家盪產。澳門政府向市民派的錢，就係香港班水魚和大陸班水魚吸過來。對全球人類而言，澳門派錢活動，都係蝕多賺少。"},{"pid":"276335d9bfa16e417b79488b11f3dd91b47c2d8a","tid":943320,"uid":141871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2693717b0e9a72b01f08887895168c8791dd83ca","tid":943320,"uid":218914,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T13:28:07.000Z","msg":"call埋我皮膚科醫生洗介賴<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Go5bgxj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGo5bgxj.jpg&h=e5104ad8&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T03:01:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">冼</span>"},{"pid":"865ab2323ccc830f153577a51b547436f4c193ce","tid":943320,"uid":34251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T03:03:13.000Z","msg":"你咁有創意又吹你唔漲"}]}